    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q038",
      "block_id": "B039",
      "text": "Thoma Bravo indicated a price of $17.25 per share, and also provided a form of equity commitment letter and draft merger agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q039",
      "block_id": "B042",
      "text": "it was no longer interested in exploring a potential transaction with the Company"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q040",
      "block_id": "B046",
      "text": "the Board authorized Barclays to advance all three parties to the second phase of the strategic process"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q041",
      "block_id": "B049",
      "text": "if it were to submit a second round bid, it would not be meaningfully higher than the price indicated in its June 9, 2016 preliminary indication of interest"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q042",
      "block_id": "B050",
      "text": "the Board established a special committee of the Board"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q043",
      "block_id": "B052",
      "text": "The Special Committee consisted of all of the non-management directors on the Board"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q044",
      "block_id": "B054",
      "text": "The Special Committee confirmed that it was not interested in pursuing a transaction at the price indicated by Sponsor A in its initial bid"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q045",
      "block_id": "B057",
      "text": "it was not interested in participating in the strategic process"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q046",
      "block_id": "B061",
      "text": "sent final bid process letters to Sponsor B and Thoma Bravo"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q047",
      "block_id": "B061",
      "text": "requesting marked drafts"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q048",
      "block_id": "B061",
      "text": "setting a final bid deadline of July 8, 2016"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q049",
      "block_id": "B066",
      "text": "if it were to submit a final bid, it would be significantly below the price indicated in its June 9, 2016 preliminary indication of interest"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q050",
      "block_id": "B067",
      "text": "pursue a proposal at price significantly below the price that Sponsor B originally indicated"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q051",
      "block_id": "B074",
      "text": "sent a revised draft of the merger agreement to Goodwin"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q052",
      "block_id": "B078",
      "text": "only Thoma Bravo submitted a bid for the Company"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q053",
      "block_id": "B078",
      "text": "bid was at a price of $19.00 per share in cash"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q054",
      "block_id": "B078",
      "text": "was prepared to execute its revised draft of the merger agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q055",
      "block_id": "B085",
      "text": "submit its best and final offer"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q056",
      "block_id": "B086",
      "text": "received a revised written, non-binding proposal from Thoma Bravo setting forth its best and final offer of $19.25 per share"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q057",
      "block_id": "B086",
      "text": "$19.25 per share was its best and final offer"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q058",
      "block_id": "B093",
      "text": "Kirkland sent Goodwin a draft of an exclusivity agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q059",
      "block_id": "B093",
      "text": "the Company would not enter into an exclusivity agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q060",
      "block_id": "B099",
      "text": "recommend to the Board that the Company enter into the merger agreement for the transaction with Thoma Bravo"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q061",
      "block_id": "B100",
      "text": "the Board unanimously adopted and declared the advisability of the merger agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q062",
      "block_id": "B101",
      "text": "the parties finalized and executed the merger agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q063",
      "block_id": "B101",
      "text": "the Company and Thoma Bravo issued a joint press release announcing the execution of the merger agreement"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q064",
      "block_id": "B048",
      "text": "it was no longer interested in exploring a potential transaction with the Company"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q065",
      "block_id": "B057",
      "text": "an acquisition of the Company would not be a strategic fit for it and that it was not interested in participating in the strategic process"
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q066",
      "block_id": "B018",
      "text": "On March 14 and March 24, 2016, the advisory committee met to discuss and consider the engagement of a financial advisor, as authorized at the March 10, 2016 Board meeting."
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q067",
      "block_id": "B018",
      "text": "The advisory committee authorized Company management to inquire whether Barclays would be available to act as a financial advisor to the Company in connection with a potential strategic transaction."
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q068",
      "block_id": "B026",
      "text": "April 19, 2016, the Company countersigned an engagement letter with Barclays, dated April 15, 2016, as authorized during the April 15, 2016 Board meeting."
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q069",
      "block_id": "B030",
      "text": "Of the parties contacted, three strategic parties and four financial sponsors executed confidentiality agreements with the Company, including Thoma Bravo on May 10, 2016."
    },
    {
      "quote_id": "Q070",
      "block_id": "B045",
      "text": "Barclays reported to the Board that at such time ten of the 11 strategic parties contacted by Barclays had declined to participate in the strategic process, and that while Strategic 3 had executed a confidentiality agreement and met with management, it did not submit a bid by the June 9, 2016 deadline."
    }
